### Variables
@hostname = localhost
@port = 3000
@baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/api

### ============================================================
### SECTION 1: SYSTEM & HEALTH (controllers/systemController.js)
### ============================================================

### 1. Test Welcome Message (The "Front Porch")
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/

### 2. Check Engine Status (Database Connection & Count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/status

### ============================================================
### SECTION 2: LOG MANAGEMENT (controllers/logController.js)
### ============================================================

### 3. Create a New Compliance Log (Expected: 201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Elevator Safety Certification - Santiago Tower",
    "category": "Maintenance",
    "status": "Passed"
}

### 4. Get ALL Logs (The full list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs

### 5. Create a 'Failed' Log (Expected: 201 Created)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Fire Alarm Certification - Expired",
    "category": "Compliance",
    "status": "Failed"
}

### 6. Query ONLY Failed Logs (Expected: 200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs?status=Failed
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### SECTION 3: VALIDATION TESTS (Data Integrity)
### ============================================================

### 7. Test Validation Failure (Missing Category) (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "This should fail because there is no category"
}

### 8. Fail Test: Invalid Category (Expected: 400 Bad Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Faulty Log",
    "category": "Pizza"
}

### 9. Test Status Default (Expected: 201 Created, Status: Pending)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Elevator Inspection - Chicago Office",
    "category": "Maintenance"
}

### 10. Test Explicit 'Passed' Status (Expected: 201 Created, Status: Passed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "action": "Annual Tax Filing - Santiago Property",
    "category": "Compliance",
    "status": "Passed"
}